{
  "stem": "33.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "The rest of us were shipped in these cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I don't know the exact number, but I think 150 would be about the right number for each one of those cars.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "The way it happened, we were standing around in this ghetto area, and they came with some horse-drawn carriages that took out-- we were allowed to take like a little knapsack, a little rucksack with us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They would take that and the people walked behind them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I remember standing around with my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And the chief of the police, Hungarian police, who was in charge of this operation, was standing with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And he was just telling some stories that, ah, oh, you will appreciate us, you know, after you left here, like, if it was our choice, of course, you know to leave.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And I remember my father, who was a very heavy smoker, he was out of cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And he sort of jokingly said that I'd give a house for a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And I knew this Hungarian chief of police, because he was in charge of organizing the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And we worked for him, basically, when we were registering people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I guess I was sort of pretty self-confident young person at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just turned around and told him-- I don't know what his rank was, captain or something-- would you please offer my father a cigarette?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I guess he was too embarrassed not to, even though he was a real maniac.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, he was a real vicious anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he did take out his cigarette case and offer my father a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think I just caught him off guard, sort of and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
